							<a href="/api/products/running-shoes">/api/products/slug</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mt-3">Note: User and Cart case slug will replace by object _id.</p>
					<a href="/doces">Check all APIs documentation</a>
				</div>
    </div>
</div>
